&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Position Summary&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Account Billing Specialist is the face of the Company for our clients.&amp;nbsp; Account Billing Specialists are responsible for maintaining great working relationships with our clients and handling their day-to-day business needs and questions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Principle Accountabilities&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
