&lt;li&gt;Assist in order processing, leveraging several different software platforms and methods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Control effective communications for your account(s) by acting as a liaison between your client(s) and various warehouse and administrative teams. This includes:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communication of inbound/outbound demand and unique client needs&lt;/li&gt;
