&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written skills (phone etiquette and fluency in English required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must possess excellent problem diagnosis and resolution skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong work ethic and a positive attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work with a high degree of autonomy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage the demands of multiple priorities simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
